query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  i.interactionType,
  i.status,
  i.executedAt,
  i.errorMessage,
  pu.postUrl,
  a.username as account_username
FROM interactions i
LEFT JOIN post_urls pu ON i.postUrlId = pu.id
LEFT JOIN accounts a ON i.fromAccountId = a.id
WHERE i.interactionType = 'like'
ORDER BY i.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10
